  <description>
    <p>
      zBridge Club is a modern, social contract bridge platform. Play with friends, compete in rated games, or practice with our advanced robot, Jethro.
    </p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Social Rooms: Play casually with friends (video/voice chat coming soon).</li>
      <li>Rated Games: Compete for ELO ratings in serious matches.</li>
      <li>Bot Practice: Hone your skills with Jethro, our 2/1 system robot.</li>
      <li>Analysis Room: Review hands and analyze play with double-dummy logic.</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
